Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.99,0:23:11.87,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur2}拜託  用更加狂烈的幻想
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.87,0:23:19.80,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur2}將我心臟染紅
